The inaugural Betway Golf Day in Kitale on Saturday thrilled hundreds of residents who turned up for the celebrations at the Kitale Golf Club.Radio Africa Group chairman Kiprono Kittony, who is also the Betway Kenya chairman, gave the keynote speech to the more than 100 golfers in attendance.Betway ambassador footballer Dennis Oliech, who was also present, caused a stir as fans flocked around him, before Nameless put up an electrifying performance until late into the night.